RESTRAINT; AUDIO RECORDINGS; TELEPHONE CALLS; FEDERAL BUREAU OF INVESTIGATION; 
POLICE MISCONDUCT; CONFIDENTIALITY; TRIALS; DRUG TRAFFICKING -- PANAMA 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
