<DATE>
<P>
November 19, 1990, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<P>
DWIGHT D EISENHOWER 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 3; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
