<TEXT>
<P>
Cincinnati Reds outfielder Eric Davis underwent arthroscopic surgery today to 
shave rough edges from the underside of his right kneecap. 
</P>
<P>
Dr. Michael Lawhon, the Reds' team physician, performed the surgery this 
morning at Christ Hospital. 
</P>
<P>
